Roles defined for the particular domain and project were received with the JWT token.
A user is created if it does not exist.
The user get the assigned roles.
The roles of the user are getting updated in the login process in the keystone database, if necccessary.
Problem: User and role definitions are note removed if a user is deactivated in keycloak.
